1.1.1.1
log
@import ports/www/horde/dimp

DIMP (Dynamic IMP) is an AJAX-like frontend for the IMP webmail system.
It provides a 3-pane layout with message preview, drag-and-drop support,
context-sensitive menus, etc.
@
